{"tid":1510821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全港最大物資站上線啦！！","createTime":"2019-08-27T10:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T06:00:39.000Z","uid":39205,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"61c7d8483d071b85841f224333ebe4e1a8896a7b","tid":1510821,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:24:25.000Z","msg":"早幾日見到有人開post想要食物卷，好多人二話不說即刻留低tg表示可以幫手，證明其實好多人想幫手。<br />\n<br />\n同朋友傾過下之後決定<span style=\"color: orange;\">開個一個平台大家交收物資</span>。形式會係類似車手channel咁，由提供物資嘅一方以填template方式pm admin，admin再post去channel入面，令有需要嘅人可以根據自己需要嘅物資同地點去pm提供嘅人作交收。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">TG channel: </span></strong><a href=\"https://t.me/hkmudg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmudg&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=b3f503e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmudg</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">提供物資方：</span></ins></strong><br />\n- 填template交比admin<br />\n- 等有人聯絡你<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">自行判斷對方是否需要幫忙</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">接收物資方：</span></ins></strong><br />\n- 睇channel有咩係自己需要同岩地點<br />\n- 㩒個tg搵對方傾<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">自行判斷對方是否可信</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>物資包括食物卷及文具等，唔接受現金！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">為咗保障大家，儘量約係多人地方交收，唔好向對方透露太多個人資訊，千祈千祈唔好講你去過邊到夢遊！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申：淨係想幫人乜鳩都唔識，有咩可以改善嘅地方希望大家留言同我講聲，再唔係pm admin。"},{"pid":"2b823920dd66f25868f8d5f0a81b42e922e302dd","tid":1510821,"uid":39205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:24:37.000Z","msg":"強調我地只係提供一個平台比大家，係唔會接受任何物資。"},{"pid":"a28907fa0c6b7574638fe9e4c88fbef1035bed08","tid":1510821,"uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1f